    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "At `onNewEpoch`, validators try to get proposer duties and attester duties. For proposer duties, we have a check that if `epoch > headEpoch + 2` then we return error as above but for attester duties, we don't have that check and blindly do `processSlots` until currentSlot.\r\n\r\nSo we need to have a check before doing `processSlots()` for attester duties, and also for other places using `processSlots()` as well.",
